OL,3,CPatients resuscitated against wishes
OL,4,Cand given drugs despite allergies
OL,6,F"We've had 'do not resuscitate' on a
OL,7,Fpatient record but because people are
OL,8,Fnot aware, people have been
OL,9,Fresuscitated. That's an extreme
OL,10,Fexample.
OL,12,F"We've had other examples where
OL,13,Freferrals have come in and people
OL,14,Fhaven't known exactly about the
OL,15,Fmedical history - issues to do with
OL,16,Fallergies and reactions to drugs and
OL,17,Fmedication are not flowing through the
OL,18,Fsystem.
