OL,6,F"Having that integrated view of
OL,7,Fislanders' health is going to be
OL,8,Finstrumental in reducing those
OL,9,Fincidents."
OL,11,FThe issues stem from there being no
OL,12,Fcentralised data system so other care
OL,13,Fproviders, such as GP practices and
OL,14,Fcharities, store their information
OL,15,Fseparately.
