OL,6,FThis makes it difficult for the
OL,7,Fhospital to easily access patient data
OL,8,Fand although serious incidents are
OL,9,Frare, officials admit people are being
OL,10,Fput at risk by the lack of a joined-up
OL,11,Fnetwork - while Jersey's health care
OL,12,Fsystem has a digital interconnectivity
OL,13,Frating of zero.
OL,15,FMr Carpenter adds: "In terms of
OL,16,Fefficiency, what I've been told by
OL,17,Fsome of the big consultants is that we
OL,18,Fcan expect to see a 15%-20%
OL,19,Fimprovement at the system level in the
OL,20,Fprovision of health and care.
