OL,3,CPatients resuscitated against wishes
OL,4,Cand given drugs despite allergies
OL,6,F"That's definitely not saying we can
OL,7,Freduce our workforce by 15%-20%, but
OL,8,Fwe can certainly improve the quality
OL,9,Fof care that we're giving to
OL,10,Fislanders."
OL,12,FHealth Minister, Deputy Tom Binet
OL,13,Fexplains: "We've got good people doing
OL,14,Fgood jobs in a number of places, but
OL,15,Fthey can't do their job properly
OL,16,Funless they've got access to all the
OL,17,Finformation they require."
